#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:2
msgid "lmcache server"
msgstr "lmcache 服务器"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:4
msgid ""
"The ``lmcache server`` command launches the standalone LMCache Multi-"
"Process (MP) server, which exposes a ZMQ control plane and an HTTP "
"frontend (status, healthcheck, cache-clear, checksum APIs). It is the "
"server that ``lmcache describe``, ``lmcache ping kvcache``, ``lmcache "
"kvcache``, and ``lmcache bench server`` talk to."
msgstr ""
"``lmcache server`` 命令启动独立的 LMCache 多进程 (MP) 服务器，该服务器暴露 ZMQ 控制平面和 HTTP 前端 "
"(状态、健康检查、清除缓存、校验和 API)。这是 ``lmcache describe``、``lmcache ping "
"kvcache``、``lmcache kvcache`` 和 ``lmcache bench server`` 进行交互的服务器。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:12
msgid ""
"This command requires the full ``lmcache`` installation with CUDA "
"extensions. It is **not** available in the lightweight ``lmcache-cli`` "
"package."
msgstr "此命令需要完整的 ``lmcache`` 安装，并带有 CUDA 扩展。它在轻量级的 ``lmcache-cli`` 包中 **不可用**。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:21
msgid "Quick start"
msgstr "快速开始"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:31
msgid "Options"
msgstr "选项"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:33
msgid ""
"The server composes its arguments from several configuration modules — "
"the multiprocess server, the storage manager (L1 / L2 adapters / "
"eviction), the HTTP frontend, and the Prometheus / telemetry "
"observability layer. The full, authoritative list is large and evolves "
"with the runtime, so consult:"
msgstr ""
"服务器从多个配置模块组合其参数——多进程服务器、存储管理器（L1 / L2 适配器 / 逐出）、HTTP 前端以及 Prometheus / "
"监控可观察性层。完整的权威列表很大，并随着运行时而变化，因此请参考："

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:42
msgid "Commonly used flags include:"
msgstr "常用的标志包括："

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:48
msgid "Flag"
msgstr "标志"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:49
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:50
msgid "``--host HOST``"
msgstr "``--host HOST``"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:51
msgid "Bind address for the server."
msgstr "服务器的绑定地址。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:52
msgid "``--port PORT``"
msgstr "``--port PORT``"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:53
msgid "ZMQ control-plane port."
msgstr "ZMQ 控制平面端口。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:54
msgid "``--chunk-size N``"
msgstr "``--chunk-size N``"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:55
msgid "KV cache chunk size in tokens."
msgstr "KV Cache 块大小（以 token 为单位）。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:56
msgid "``--l1-size-gb GB``"
msgstr "``--l1-size-gb GB``"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:57
msgid "L1 (CPU/DRAM) cache capacity in GB."
msgstr "L1 (CPU/DRAM) 缓存容量（以 GB 为单位）。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:58
msgid "``--eviction-policy POLICY``"
msgstr "``--eviction-policy POLICY``"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:59
msgid "L1 eviction policy (e.g. ``LRU``)."
msgstr "L1 逐出策略（例如 ``LRU``）。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:60
msgid "``--eviction-trigger-watermark RATIO``"
msgstr "``--eviction-trigger-watermark RATIO``"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:61
msgid "L1 fill ratio at which eviction begins."
msgstr "开始逐出的 L1 填充比率。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:62
msgid "``--eviction-ratio RATIO``"
msgstr "``--eviction-ratio RATIO``"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:63
msgid "Fraction of L1 cleared per eviction cycle."
msgstr "每个逐出周期清除的 L1 分数。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:64
msgid "``--max-workers N``"
msgstr "``--max-workers N``"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:65
msgid "Number of server worker processes."
msgstr "服务器工作进程的数量。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:66
msgid "``--coordinator-url URL``"
msgstr "``--coordinator-url URL``"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:67
msgid ""
"Register with an MP coordinator at this base URL (e.g. "
"``http://coordinator:9300``). Opt-in; enables fleet registration. See "
":doc:`/mp/coordinator`."
msgstr ""
"在此基础 URL（例如 ``http://coordinator:9300``）注册 MP 协调器。可选；启用车队注册。请参见 "
":doc:`/mp/coordinator`。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:70
msgid "``--coordinator-advertise-ip IP``"
msgstr "``--coordinator-advertise-ip IP``"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:71
msgid ""
"IP the coordinator should reach this server at (defaults to the outbound "
"IP)."
msgstr "协调器应通过此服务器访问的 IP（默认为出站 IP）。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:73
msgid "``--coordinator-heartbeat-interval SECONDS``"
msgstr "``--coordinator-heartbeat-interval SECONDS``"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:74
msgid ""
"Seconds between heartbeats (``> 0``, default ``5``). Keep well below the "
"coordinator's instance timeout."
msgstr "心跳之间的秒数（``> 0``，默认值为 ``5``）。应远低于协调器的实例超时。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:76
msgid "``--coordinator-l2-event-reporting``"
msgstr "``--coordinator-l2-event-reporting``"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:77
msgid ""
"Enable reporting L2 store/lookup events to the coordinator for fleet-wide"
" usage tracking and quota-based eviction."
msgstr "启用将 L2 存储/查找事件报告给协调器，以便进行全队列使用跟踪和基于配额的逐出。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:79
msgid "``--coordinator-l2-event-flush-interval SECONDS``"
msgstr "``--coordinator-l2-event-flush-interval SECONDS``"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:80
msgid "Seconds between L2 event batch flushes (``> 0``, default ``1``)."
msgstr "L2 事件批量刷新之间的秒数（``> 0``，默认 ``1``）。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:81
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``--trace-level {storage}``"
msgstr "``--trace-level {storage}``"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:82
msgid "Enable storage-level trace recording (see :doc:`trace`)."
msgstr "启用存储级别的追踪记录（请参见 :doc:`trace`）。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:83
msgid "``--trace-output PATH``"
msgstr "``--trace-output PATH``"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:84
msgid "Destination for recorded ``.lct`` trace files."
msgstr "记录的 ``.lct`` 跟踪文件的目标。"

#: ../../source/cli/server.rst:86
msgid ""
"L2 adapters, observability, and Prometheus exporters are configured "
"through their own flag groups; see ``lmcache server --help`` for the "
"complete set."
msgstr ""
"L2 适配器、可观察性和 Prometheus 导出器通过各自的标志组进行配置；有关完整的设置，请参见 ``lmcache server "
"--help``。"

